OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FA great-grandmother thought to have
OL,7,Finoperable cancer has become the first
OL,8,Fperson in the UK to receive treatment
OL,9,Fusing a novel technique.
OL,11,FBrenda Iveson, from Harrogate in North
OL,12,FYorkshire, was told that usual cancer
OL,13,Ftreatments would not work for the six-
OL,14,Fcentimetre tumour in her liver.
OL,16,FBut medics at Leeds Teaching Hospitals
OL,17,FNHS Trust offered the 92-year-old a
OL,18,Fminimally invasive procedure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FShe was given robotic-guided
OL,7,Felectrochemotherapy ` a treatment that
OL,8,Fcombines a small dose of chemotherapy
OL,9,Fwith targeted electrical pulses.
OL,11,FSurgeons used robotic needle guidance
OL,12,Fto precisely place needles around the
OL,13,Ftumour to help direct the treatment in
OL,14,Fa pioneering move that has never been
OL,15,Fperformed in the UK before.
OL,17,FNow Mrs Iveson's tumour has shrunk by
OL,18,Faround 80%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FBecause of the location of her tumour,
OL,7,Fas well as her frailty, Mrs Iveson was
OL,8,Ftold "nothing could be done" when she
OL,9,Fwas diagnosed in late 2025.
OL,11,FSurgery, chemotherapy and radiotherapy
OL,12,Fwere all deemed unsuitable.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FBut when Professor Tze Min Wah,
OL,7,Fresearch and innovation lead for the
OL,8,Finterventional oncology programme at
OL,9,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust and
OL,10,Fprofessor of interventional radiology
OL,11,Fat the University of Leeds, saw Mrs
OL,12,FIveson's case, she realised that the
OL,13,Fpioneering treatment could offer hope
OL,14,Fto Mrs Iveson and her family.
OL,16,FClinicians used robotic needle
OL,17,Fguidance to precisely place needles
OL,18,Faround the tumour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FThe technology helps improve the
OL,7,Faccuracy of the electrochemotherapy,
OL,8,Fparticularly for tumours in complex or
OL,9,Fhard-to-reach areas.
OL,11,FThe treatment was carried out under
OL,12,Fgeneral anaesthetic and does not use
OL,13,Fheat, which means it can safely treat
OL,14,Ftumours located close to vital
OL,15,Fstructures such as blood vessels and
OL,16,Fbile ducts.
OL,18,FIt is the first time this treatment
OL,19,Fhas been delivered alongside the
OL,20,Frobotic guidance in a liver in the UK,
OL,21,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FMrs Iveson said: "I had been told
OL,7,Fthere was nothing that could be done.
OL,9,F"So to be offered this treatment gave
OL,10,Fme real hope.
OL,12,F"I'm so glad I went ahead ` it wasn't
OL,13,Fpainful or debilitating, and I feel
OL,14,Fvery well."
OL,16,FProfessor Wah said: "This treatment
OL,17,Fallowed us to offer an option where
OL,18,Fthere would otherwise have been none.
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@AOUtD@AOUvD@KO]xD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,F"The addition of robotic guidance
OL,7,Fimproves precision and opens up new
OL,8,Fpossibilities, particularly for
OL,9,Fpatients with tumours in difficult
OL,10,Flocations or who are not suitable for
OL,11,Fother treatments."
OL,13,FShe told the Press Association:
OL,14,F"Introducing robotic guidance really
OL,15,Fhelped with this particular case, the
OL,16,Fneedles provided more accurate
OL,17,Fplacement and made the treatment times
OL,18,Fshorter ` she is the UK first for the
OL,19,Frobotic guidance to insert the
OL,20,Felectrode chemotherapy needles into
OL,21,Fthe tumour for treatment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,F"She is doing well and she is very
OL,7,Fgrateful that she has had this
OL,8,Ftreatment because otherwise she did
OL,9,Fnot have any other options."
OL,11,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust is
OL,12,Fcurrently the only hospital in the UK
OL,13,Fdelivering liver cancer
OL,14,Felectrochemotherapy as part of a
OL,15,FEuropean research study.
OL,17,FThe study is assessing the safety and
OL,18,Fefficacy of the treatment for patients
OL,19,Fwith liver cancer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FIt is also examining the impact of
OL,7,Fsurvival, quality of life and pain.
OL,9,FMrs Iveson, who has been happily
OL,10,Fmarried for 70 years, said: "Research
OL,11,Fmay offer real results when there are
OL,12,Fno other options.
OL,14,F"You're looked after so well, and it's
OL,15,Fhow medicine moves forward.
OL,17,F"If it helps me and future patients,
OL,18,Fthen it's worth it."
OL,26,@rD@]OUvD@AOUyD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780275788
OL,3,CGreat-grandmother gets UK-first cancer
OL,4,Ctreatment on tumour deemed untreatable
OL,6,FCurrent scans show that Mrs Iveson's
OL,7,Ftumour is in a stable condition and
OL,8,Fshe is being monitored closely by
OL,9,Fexperts at the hospital trust.
OL,11,F"We are all happy that something could
OL,12,Fbe done that might prolong my life and
OL,13,Fwhich was not painful or debilitating
OL,14,Fin any way," Mrs Iveson added.
OL,16,F"It seems to be a very effective
OL,17,Ftreatment and particularly useful in
OL,18,Folder patients who are frail."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@LO]xD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
